permissions.name: com.readystatesoftware.ghostlog.permission.READ_LOGS
permissions.label: read logcat output for Ghost Log integrated apps
permissions.description: Allows an application to read the logcat output for Ghost Log integrated apps. This allows it to discover general information about integrated apps that is being written to the log.

manifest:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>

	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="14" android:targetSdkVersion="19" />
	<permission android:label="read logcat output for Ghost Log integrated apps" android:name="com.readystatesoftware.ghostlog.permission.READ_LOGS" android:protectionLevel="0x0" android:description="Allows an application to read the logcat output for Ghost Log integrated apps. This allows it to discover general information about integrated apps that is being written to the log." />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_LOGS" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.GET_TASKS" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_SUPERUSER" />
	<uses-permission android:name="com.readystatesoftware.ghostlog.permission.READ_LOGS" />
	<application android:theme="resourceId:0x7f080000" android:label="Ghost Log" android:icon="res/drawable-mdpi/ic_launcher.png" android:allowBackup="true">

		</activity>
